Package com.arthenica.mobileffmpeg

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LogCallback
    Represents a callback function to redirect logs.
    StatisticsCallback
    Represents a callback function to receive statistics of running operation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbiDetect
    This class is used to detect running ABI name using Android's cpufeatures library.
    Config
    This class is used to configure MobileFFmpeg library utilities/tools.
    FFmpeg
    Main class for FFmpeg operations.
    LogMessage
    Represents a redirected log message.
    MediaInformation
    Media information class.
    MediaInformationParser
    Helper class for MediaInformation.
    Statistics
    Represents statistics data.
    StreamInformation
    Stream information class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Abi
    Helper enumeration type for Android ABIs; includes only supported ABIs.
    Level
    Helper enumeration type for log levels.
